social_posts.post_text: When it’s time for the @lifechurchgreenbay Staff Christmas Party? This is how @sonnyrhennessy rolls out!
Trimming the tree with @sonnyrhennessy @isaiahhennessy45 @aubree.hennessy Moses & Louis. Nowhere I’d rather be!
null

We’re so grateful for all the items that have been donated through our Amazon Wishlist. Bedding, dishes and a CHAINSAW!! We still need your help though. If you still have any end of the year giving you need to allocate I’d love it if you’d consider. Link to the wishlist is in my bio.

I’m beyond grateful to everyone who has already given to The Reserve - our property dedicated to restoring broken people! It’s SO encouraging! The property is already being renovated and items are coming in off our @amazon wishlist (link to wishlist is in my bio). It’s not too late to give a 2022 tax deductible gift. Our first intensives start in just a few weeks and there’s already a waiting list of people waiting to go through @j2_wholeness  and be restored! The harvest really IS plentiful. Thanks again! @sonnyrhennessy  @thenehemiahproject  #happynewyear

I couldn’t help but weep as I heard @dorlovsky pray openly and out loud for Damar on @espn. The power of the Holy Spirit came through the screen. Thank you brother for being courageous and listening to that still small voice! Let it be so Lord - let it be so!

We’re down to the wire here @the_reserve_nc getting ready for our first guests from to arrive tomorrow so we added a new Project Manager to keep us on track. Maggie Doll from @thenehemiahproject. Things are looking up!
@seattlekraken!!!! Let’s gooooo!!! #sleeplessinseattle
Reminds me of a classic @patschatz sermon. #holyghosttwister
Do you or someone you know need an intensive? We have a few slots open for upcoming sessions. Dates listed on our website.  @theexchangecollaborative @the_reserve_nc @sonnyrhennessy
@pastorkeene is bringing it this morning @lifechurchgreenbay!
I couldn’t be more proud watching @aubree.hennessy be a part of leading worship @newlifechurchvaughan this weekend. It’s only just begun!
Larnelle Harris is the Luther Vandross of Christian music. There - I said it!

A little more than 11 years after his promotion to Heaven, Pastor Buntain still remains the single biggest influence on my life. I love and miss him everyday. You never know the impact you’re having. If you’ve got a broken spirit or relationships today - “It’s never too late to begin again”
null

I’m so excited to speak for my brother @theallengriffin & my sister @hushini tomorrow @wsfirst! Almost exactly 26 years ago - in July of 1997 - I preached my first sermon here while on my internship. This church changed @sonnyrhennessy & my life! It expanded our vision for what church could really be! @lifechurchgreenbay wouldn’t be what it is today without this place!  If you’re in the Piedmont Triad area - come see me!

Such good insight and teaching from 
@sonnyrhennessy on demonic activity. Have you been feeling or experiencing this? You are not alone. We are at war! We wrestle - not against flesh & blood - but against the powers of darkness. Prepare & equip yourself. If you’re feeling overwhelmed? DM either Sonny or me, or reach out to @theexchangecollaborative
Read full blog at:
sonnyhennessy.com
Pastor @ddeguara from @rlcsac bringing a prophetic WORD this morning @lifechurchgreenbay! “Strategic Praise” Y’all better get here at 10:45! #shifthappens
New Episode out now on whichever platform you listen to your podcasts. @sonnyrhennessy #spiritualwarfare #endtimes
Y’all! Pastor @becky.alcantar just brought a WORD @lifechurchgreenbay! You NEED to get here at 10:45! Oh and she got to stompin in her Air Force Ones! #teachustopray
“You will never manifest what only God can provide.” @becky.alcantar @lifechurchgreenbay #standdownprayers #teachustopray
“God may not give you more money when you tithe but He WILL do more with the money you have” @dallasjcox @lifechurchgreenbay #generosity #comeonsomebody

Happy Anniversary to these 2 crazy kids. Through thick & thin they’ve grown up together and proved that in the end love really does conquer all. I can say with 100% honesty that 62 years in - they love each other and Jesus more than ever! I love dad & mom!

What a weekend! I couldn’t have asked for a better 50th Birthday Celebration! @sonnyrhennessy pulled out all the stops! First she surprised me by flying the joys of my life @aubree.hennessy & @isaiahhennessy45 in from college to have a birthday dinner @republicchophouse and to spend the weekend with me. Saturday we thrifted, went to the @packersproshop, watched the @uw_football beat the @oregonfootball and played a killer game of @scrabble. This morning we all got to be @lifechurchgreenbay for services together where I was surprised with @aubree.hennessy leading a song and @isaiahhennessy45 giving a presentation on the mic to honor me and sing me Happy Birthday. Then I was overwhelmed with emotion as I sat and watched a video of my spiritual mother Lorraine Buntain wishing me a Happy Birthday. Then my brother from another mother Barry Edgemon @fatherseekers_ brought the house down with a killer message. He then picked me up and took me for ANOTHER dinner @republicchophouse. Just when I thought the night was done I walked into @theexchangecoffee where so many of my closest friends were hiding and threw a crazy surprise birthday party for me. I just can’t even put into the words how loved and honored I feel. My heart is full! Thank you to @dallasjcox & @jessicahogan626 for being the MC’s for the night, @sncox for catering it with out of this world food, and everyone for all the kind words, wishes and gifts. Most of all thank you @sonnyrhennessy for making me feel like the king of the world! #yearofjubilee
I’ve been thinking about this @chickfila Honey Pepper Pimento sandwich for 40 days! It was worth the wait! #eatmorechicken

Such a great book by @stevejonesspk & @lucas_jadin. Practical, challenging, inspiring, and easy to read. By the final chapters I found myself cheering the characters on like I was watching a movie. Well worth your time! #thetwinthieves

Happy 248th Birthday to the United States Marine Corp. Thank you seems insufficient for all the men & women who have so selflessly served & sacrificed for our freedom. You are heroes, you are appreciated and you are loved! Semper Fi! #thefewtheproud

I’ve always had such a deep love & admiration for the men & women who’ve chosen to serve in the Armed Forces. Today, as I pray for the hearts & minds of those who’ve sacrificed so much to protect our hopes & dreams I am overwhelmed with gratitude. Thank you for covering me with your courage. I love you! #selflessservice

Got to spend a little time with this guy today! @steelers Chaplain @kentchevalier. This guy inspires me. He’s a great leader, disciple maker, husband and father. He is raising the bar for what it means to be an @nfl Chaplain!
So cool watching @crosbykicks2 nail a FG to end the first half for the @nygiants

Happy Birthday to @aubree.hennessy - my favorite girl in the whole wide world. You are a miracle in motion. The enemy has been trying to take you out since you were in the womb - but you won’t quit - you won’t be defeated - you are more than a conqueror! You are loving & kind, gracious & tenacious, tender & compassionate, tough as nails. No one can make me laugh like you do! You are beautiful & gifted but humble & patient. Your compassionate heart challenges & inspires me. I’ve told you this privately but I post it publicly today - you are going to impact the world through the songs you sing and the songs you write. People all over the world are going to sing YOUR songs. You carry an anointing the world has seldom seen. You are a woman of virtue & valor - truly a Proverbs 31 girl. There’s nothing I’m more proud of than being your dad. You make me better! I love you. Happy One Nine Bear! #daddysgirl
